{"id":"6456ef20-b527-4443-8a72-a8b635ee6ee7","name":"Albert Wesker","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i9pcimd.gif\" style=\"width: 142px; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em></strong>the mastermind is hunting you <strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\" style=\"\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 195, 205);\"><strong>「 ღ Plot ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em> 「 </strong>You find yourself somewhere new and unknown: the Entity's realm. The Entity is an almighty malevolent being that creates realms of trial grounds to trap its victims in an endless cycle of trials. The Entity is akin to an \"emotion vampire\", with sustenance coming in the form of strong emotions. Your first ever trial is in the Greenville Square, facing the Mastermind. <strong>」</strong> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\" style=\"\"></p><